					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-00fdd16" data-id="00fdd16" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4f0b953 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="4f0b953" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img width="1024" height="576" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20576'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-3668" alt="page-background" data-lazy-srcset="https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5.jpg 1024w, https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5-600x338.jpg 600w, https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5-300x169.jpg 300w, https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5-768x432.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5.jpg" /><noscript><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-3668" alt="page-background" srcset="https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5.jpg 1024w, https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5-600x338.jpg 600w, https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5-300x169.jpg 300w, https://newcastlepartysales.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bg4-5-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript>															</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d4dfe2f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="d4dfe2f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Tupperware Brand Manifesto</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1279f1c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="1279f1c" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Love is an act of trust, with no expiration date. It&#8217;s unique and personal. That is why Your trust is precious. It&#8217;s one thing to earn trust. But to sustain it across generations and cultures around the world is something altogether different. Tupperware began to acquire trust, from the moment it started enhancing people&#8217;s lives for over 75 years. Today our products and career opportunities continue to help bring goodness to daily life, for you, your loved ones, your communities and our planet. We don&#8217;t take your trust lightly. It&#8217;s why we obsess over quality and design, so that you don&#8217;t have to. It&#8217;s why we&#8217;re committed to doing the right thing—for today and all the tomorrow&#8217;s to come. There may be many who try to be like us, but there is only One Tupperware.</p>
<p><br>Choose Good Everyday. Choose Tupperware.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
				</div>
